- Cohesive, album‑first sequencing: The Fleetwood Mac candidate explicitly promises “cohesive start‑to‑finish sequencing” and an immersive, front‑to‑back listening experience. That directly matches my strong preference for single‑artist albums that reward repeat play and thoughtful sequencing — a primary deciding factor for me.
